<div data-type="glossary"><h3 data-type="glossary-title">Glossary</h3>
<dl id="fs-idm39818672">
<dt>halide</dt>
<dd id="fs-idm38577264">compound containing an anion of a group 17 element in the 1&#8722; oxidation state (fluoride, F<sup>&#8722;</sup>; chloride, Cl<sup>&#8722;</sup>; bromide, Br<sup>&#8722;</sup>; and iodide, I<sup>&#8722;</sup>)</dd>
</dl>
<dl id="fs-idm15345952">
<dt>interhalogen</dt>
<dd id="fs-idp1050528">compound formed from two or more different halogens</dd>
</dl>
